            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Chronolgical data: Probably the inscription was realized during the second half of the first century AD, but before the year 89, when the cohors got the titles &amp;quot;&amp;quot;pia&amp;quot;&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;&amp;quot;fidelis&amp;quot;&amp;quot; by Domitian. (B): Bruhl: Z. 2: Pom&amp;lt;e&amp;gt;(ptina).</p>
            </div>
